**Relevant Ghanaian policies**

- [Ghana’s Forest and Wildlife Policy, 2012](http://extwprlegs1.fao.org/docs/pdf/gha144198.pdf);

- [Forestry Development Master Plan, 2016-2036](http://extwprlegs1.fao.org/docs/pdf/gha174385.pdf);

- [National Forest Plantation Strategy, 2016-2040](https://www.oldwebsite.fcghana.org/userfiles/files/Plantation%20Annual%20Report/Ghana%20Forest%20Plantation%20Strategy_24_01_16%20(2).pdf);

- [Ghana REDD+ Strategy, 2016-2035](http://extwprlegs1.fao.org/docs/pdf/gha178876.pdf);

- [Forest and Wildlife Resources Management Plans](https://www.clientearth.org/media/fhbpsk10/2012-01-01-ghana-forest-and-wildlife-policy-2012-ext-en.pdf);

- [Ghana’s Cocoa-Forest REDD+ Programme](https://www.forestcarbonpartnership.org/system/files/documents/1b.%20Ghana%20overview.pdf);

- [Ghana Forest Investment Programme](https://mlnr.gov.gh/index.php/programs-projects/ghana-forest-investment-program-fip/); 
  and


- [Ghana Wood Tracking System and Legality Assurance System](https://www.oldwebsite.fcghana.org/fctvd/index.php/focal-areas/wood-tracking-system).
